rows.label: tlk42410111_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Something both sad and
happy happened... mo.

rows.label: tlk42410111_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Now that I've come to like
salvaging, I was dreaming of
one day salvaging in Acedia, mo.

rows.label: tlk42410111_04_msg0003
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]But now I can't go to Acedia, mo!

rows.label: tlk42410111_04_msg0004
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]At this rate, I can't get
any Acedian treasure, mo!

rows.label: tlk42410111_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Just as I was lamenting, Rimurimu
told me something good, mo.

rows.label: tlk42410111_04_msg0006
rows.name:
Apparently, you can get
similar treasures in the
Liberalitas Archipelago, mo.

rows.label: tlk42410111_04_msg0007
rows.name:
The location is close, so it
seems I didn't need to be so
fixated on Acedia after all, mo!
